Duff and Phelps Selected Utilities Incsaid it approved payment of higher monthly dividends.    The closed end-investment company approved payment of 4.5cts on April 10, record March 31; of five cts, payable May 11,record April 30; and of 5.5 cts, payable June 10, record May29.    Duff and Phelps first monthly dividend of four cts was paidon March 10, it noted. Reuter&#3;